o estimate the contribution of such SNRs to, e.g. the galactic energy\nbalance and the momentum-injection into the surrounding interstellar medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2015 10:25:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-24"}
