 strongholds duration is also systematically characterized in the SIRM\nmodel. The results compare well with the electoral results data revealing an\nexponential decay in the persistence of the strongholds with time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Mar 2015 15:48:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-29"}
